  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK907">
<l>peṇṇēval ceytoḻuku māṇmaiyi ṉāṇuṭaip </l>
<l> peṇṇē perumai yuṭaittu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even shame faced womanhood is more to be esteemed than the shameless manhood that performs the behests of a wife.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
